lines.text:
[Referring to her son, Alexander, revealed as new Antichrist and world leader]
That freak will never rule, because I'm gonna kill him!
You made me a surrogate for Delia's brother, you son of a bitch!
The good news is - you got your baby! No more testing, isn't that a relief.
Just my annual Pap smear!
That's riiiight.
[last lines]
I wanna see my son
[last lines]
Yes mother... See Him... Really See Him
[She tries to shoot them both only for the gun to turn round and fire at her]
A dishonest cop
Ex... Ex...
What's this world coming too?
Going straight to hell... straight to hell
Can he be stopped? Is there hope?
If there wasn't I'd pack it in right now
Father, the antichrist has always been described as a male... does it have to be.
Well the bible wasn't meant to be sexist... mankind can also mean womankind.

[echoing his words]
Womankind! Womankind!
Our Hell is His Paradise
